"Alll right" Wildrider yells, bashing Speedbreaker as he puts his hands up.
"Someone who thinks like us, ha ha ha hhah" he screams bringing out his own
gun and leveling it to the air, pulling the trigger multiple times, each
trigger pull, 25 laser beams spurt out. "KNOCK IT OFF" screams Motormaster
flailing a fist into Wildrider sending him back, and the hit Stunticon
cackles all the way to the ground. "It has begun" states Dead-End silently.

Astroblast smiled widely. "Okay boys settle down, anyways, Motormaster, we
were able to use stasis pods to make bodies for the two personality
components we stole from the Predacon base before we left" he says,
pointing to the two cassetes. "Every one say hi, to Beastbox and
Squawktalk" with that he presses a button activating the tape.
